erb between a verb and "with" in the "V with" construction. For example, "she should go with" is acceptable while "she should go quickly with" is not. This is why the "with" in the "V with" construction is classified as a particle.%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c Now, let us finish with a meme at this link: %0a%3c %0a%3c https://ygdp.yale.edu/sites/default/files/images/come%2520with%2520meme.png%0a%3c %0a%3c Source: https://ygdp.yale.edu/phenomena/come-with%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Expansions:%0a%3c [[#expansions]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#expansionsend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a%3c %0a%3c (:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:else:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Comments%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c (:section: F:)%0a%3c (:Category: MorphosyntacticDiversity:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
